## Set Up Multi-Factor Authentication (MFA)

After password reset, you'll be prompted to set up MFA:

### Option A: Microsoft Authenticator App (Recommended)

1. Download Microsoft Authenticator app from your app store
2. When prompted in portal, click "Set up another way"
3. Select "Authenticator app"
4. Scan the QR code with your app
5. Enter the code shown in the app to verify

